<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Gerador de QR Code com API</title>
    <style>
        *{
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        body {
            background:linear-gradient(90deg ,  rgb(79, 161, 194) , rgb(8, 103, 134) ) ;
            display:flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;

        }
.container{
    margin-top: 50px;
    width: 400px;
    height: 550px;
   
    display:flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
  box-shadow: 0px 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}
#form {
    
    height: 50%;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
}
h1 {
    padding-top: 10px;
    margin-bottom: -40px;
}
input{
  width: 80%;
  font-size: 16px;
  padding: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
  border-radius: 10px;
}
input:focus, textarea:focus {
  border-color: #007bff;
  box-shadow: 0 0 3px #007bff;
}
input::placeholder, textarea::placeholder {
  color: #888;
  font-style: italic;
}
button {
  background-color: #007bff;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 4px;
  cursor: pointer;
  margin-bottom: -50px;
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  input, textarea {
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .container {
    width: 350px;
  }
}
h5 {
color:gray;
    margin-left: 15px;
    margin-right: 15px;

}
#qrcode {
   padding-bottom: 20px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Gerador de QR Code</h1>
      
        <div id="form">
            <input type="text" id="text-input" placeholder="Texto ou URL para converter...">
            <button onclick="generateQRCode()">Gerar QR Code</button>
        </div>
        <div id="qrcode"></div>
        <h5>Para usar o gerador de códigos QR, basta seguir estes passos:
<br><br>
            - Insira o texto desejado no campo de entrada <br><br>
           - Clique no botão "Gerar QR Code".<br><br>
           - O código QR correspondente será gerado e exibido na página.<br><br></h5>
    </div>



    <script>
        function generateQRCode() {
            var text = document.getElementById('text-input').value;
            var apiUrl = 'https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=150x150&data=' + encodeURIComponent(text);
            var img = document.createElement('img');
            img.src = apiUrl;
            document.getElementById('qrcode').innerHTML = '';
            document.getElementById('qrcode').appendChild(img);
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
